  "instructions": [
    "Cut the little gem lettuce into wedges and set aside.",
    "Peel and thinly slice the red onion and red bell pepper.",
    "Seed and thinly slice the orange bell pepper.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the red wine vinegar and olive oil.",
    "Add the sliced onion, red bell pepper, and orange bell pepper to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Add the chopped cilantro to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Arrange the lettuce wedges on a platter and spoon the mirepoix mixture over the top.",
    "Serve immediately."
